/* 05_mantissa.sql.in — mantissa-packed payload pack/unpack.
 *
 * Per ADR 0012: high 64 bits of a hash pack into one coordinate's
 * mantissa, low 64 bits into another — substrate-specific read pattern
 * justifying the hash128_t {hi, lo} struct in C (per RULES.md R22).
 *
 * Real wrappers land Chunk 1 Story 1.7. */

